### Installation:

After clone this repository

```bash
$ sudo npm install -g ionic cordova
$npm install

```

Then, to run it

```bash

In the  Browser
$ionic lab


For Android Platform 
$ cordova platform add android
$cordova run android

For Ios platform 
$  cordova platform add ios
$  cordova run ios
```

